SetInCountry: Canada
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Gobind  Singh
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I promised to my wife that we will go out of country after marriage but I have
  done 1 year of my marriage life even I could not fullfill dream because of some
  problem so in this way we got fight every and she always get hurt from me which
  I do not like hence in this way I am trying to fulfil her dream doo let's see how
  I m lucky .
